Abstract = {{This paper proposes a new framework that takes advantage of the
   computing capabilities provided by the Internet of Thing (IoT) paradigm
   in order to support collaborative applications. It looks at the
   requirements needed to run a wide range of computing tasks on a set of
   devices in the user environment with limited computing resources. This
   approach contributes to building the social dimension of the IoT by
   enabling the addition of computing resources accessible to the user
