Abstract = {{A smart city enhances the quality of its citizens' lives by providing
   ease of access to ubiquitous services through integration using
   communication systems at the foundation. Additionally, ITS plays a major
   role in making a metropolitan area into a smart city. The current
   IP-based solutions for ITS have slanted the performance due to high
   demand for data on the move, especially when the consumers become the
