   CO2 emissions and other pollutants are being documented. Maximizing on
   the centralized nature of the China's government, implemented Chinese
   pollution, climate changes mitigation and adaptation initiatives,
   ``SMART' strategies and credible measures are promising. A good and
   practical example is the interactive and dynamic website and database
   covering 367 Chinese cities and providing real time information on
   environmental and pollution emissions AO. Also, water quality index
