Abstract = {{This letter introduces timing channels in connectionless Bluetooth low
   energy (BLE). The proposed standard-compliant enhancement, BLE with
   timing channels (BLE-TC), improves the energy efficiency of an
   energy-constrained connectionless BLE transmitter by encoding additional
   information in the interarrival time between BLE advertisements. BLE-TC
   is analytically compared with the connectionless BLE standard. Using
